{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-index-js","path":"/emperor-yuryaku/","webpackCompilationHash":"7a029579674444588069","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Shin-tech25's blog","author":"Shin-tech25","siteUrl":"https://Shin-tech25.netlify.app"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"73f135a6-ed8c-524b-af16-5a9159b41092","excerpt":"…","html":"<h1 id=\"雄略天皇\">雄略天皇</h1>\n<p>雄略天皇は五世紀の人物です。中国の歴史書（＝宋書倭国伝）では、「倭王武」と記載されており、埼玉県の稲荷山古墳から出土した辛亥名鉄剣の銘文に見える「獲加多支鹵大王」が「記紀」にいう「ワカタケル」天皇すなわち雄略天皇であることはほぼ確実だと考えられています。</p>\n<p>猪狩りをする雄略天皇（安達吟光画）\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c24acd84181e37b1610ef269c4627dd3/625ec/Tenno_Yuryaku.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.63306451612904%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"猪狩りをする雄略天皇（安達吟光画）\"\n        title=\"猪狩りをする雄略天皇（安達吟光画）\"\n        src=\"/static/c24acd84181e37b1610ef269c4627dd3/a296c/Tenno_Yuryaku.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c24acd84181e37b1610ef269c4627dd3/f544b/Tenno_Yuryaku.jpg 200w,\n/static/c24acd84181e37b1610ef269c4627dd3/41689/Tenno_Yuryaku.jpg 400w,\n/static/c24acd84181e37b1610ef269c4627dd3/a296c/Tenno_Yuryaku.jpg 800w,\n/static/c24acd84181e37b1610ef269c4627dd3/625ec/Tenno_Yuryaku.jpg 992w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n出典 Wikipedia</p>\n<h2 id=\"宋書倭国伝\">宋書倭国伝</h2>\n<p>宋書倭国伝には、倭の五王（大和政権の大王（おおきみ））が、中国に認めてもらい朝鮮半島に対する影響力を強めて、国（ヤマト政権）を発展させようとした経緯が記されています。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">…興死して弟武立つ。自ら使持節都督倭・百済・新羅・任那・加羅・秦韓・慕韓七国く諸軍事安東大将軍倭国王称す。</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 246px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8f14b0e91bb95060077b9310d146dfda/52e6c/soujyowakokuden.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 126.01626016260161%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"宋書倭国伝\"\n        title=\"宋書倭国伝\"\n        src=\"/static/8f14b0e91bb95060077b9310d146dfda/52e6c/soujyowakokuden.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8f14b0e91bb95060077b9310d146dfda/f544b/soujyowakokuden.jpg 200w,\n/static/8f14b0e91bb95060077b9310d146dfda/52e6c/soujyowakokuden.jpg 246w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 246px) 100vw, 246px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"稲荷山古墳から出土した辛亥名鉄剣\">稲荷山古墳から出土した辛亥名鉄剣</h2>\n<h1 id=\"参考\">参考</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://sekainorekisi.com/glossary/%E9%9B%84%E7%95%A5%E5%A4%A9%E7%9A%87/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">世界の歴史まっぷ 雄略天皇</a></li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/emperor-yuryaku/#%E9%9B%84%E7%95%A5%E5%A4%A9%E7%9A%87\">雄略天皇</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/emperor-yuryaku/#%E5%AE%8B%E6%9B%B8%E5%80%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%BC%9D\">宋書倭国伝</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/emperor-yuryaku/#%E7%A8%B2%E8%8D%B7%E5%B1%B1%E5%8F%A4%E5%A2%B3%E3%81%8B%E3%82%89%E5%87%BA%E5%9C%9F%E3%81%97%E3%81%9F%E8%BE%9B%E4%BA%A5%E5%90%8D%E9%89%84%E5%89%A3\">稲荷山古墳から出土した辛亥名鉄剣</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/emperor-yuryaku/#%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83\">参考</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/emperor-yuryaku"},"frontmatter":{"title":"冊封体制と五世紀の東アジアの勢力図","date":"2022-07-25","description":"五世紀の日本を雄略天皇を軸に考えます。冊封体制や東アジア勢力図についても。","tags":["日本史","雄略天皇"],"slug":"emperor-yuryaku"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/emperor-yuryaku","relatedPosts":[],"latestPosts":[{"title":"GitHub Actionsの基礎","slug":"github-actions-basic","date":"2022-07-25"},{"title":"Gatsby＋GitHub Actions+Ansibleで自分メディアを作った","slug":"gatsby-cicd-markdown-blog","date":"2022-07-25"},{"title":"Gatsbyで内部リンクをSPA的に使う方法","slug":"gatsby-internal-link","date":"2022-07-24"},{"title":"Google検索のオプションなど","slug":"google-search","date":"2022-07-24"},{"title":"ハッキングにおける偵察技術","slug":"hacking-reconnaissance","date":"2022-07-24"}],"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/gatsby-internal-link"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Gatsbyで内部リンクをSPA的に使う方法","date":"2022-07-24","tags":["Gatsby","ブログ","内部リンク","SPA"],"slug":"gatsby-internal-link","keywords":"Gatsby, ブログ, 内部リンク, SPA"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/gatsby-cicd-markdown-blog"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Gatsby＋GitHub Actions+Ansibleで自分メディアを作った","date":"2022-07-25","tags":["ブログ","静的サイト","Gatsby","Ansible","GitHub Actions","Git"],"slug":"gatsby-cicd-markdown-blog","keywords":"Gatsby, GitHub Actions, GitHub, git, CICD, 静的サイトジェネレーター, 静的サイト, Ansible, Markdown"}}}}}